{{File sharing sidebar}}
[[File:Rättegången_mot_TPB_-_2009-02-16_(gabbe).jpg|260px]]
'''海盜灣'''（{{lang-en|The Pirate Bay}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：{{lang|en|TPB}}）是一個專門儲存、分類及搜尋[[BitTorrent_(协议)|Bittorrent]][[种子文件|种子文件]]及[[磁力連結|磁力連結]]的[[網站|網站]]，由[[瑞典|瑞典]]的民間[[反著作權|反版權]]組織{{tsl|en|Piratbyrån||海盜署}}於2003年成立，支持35种语言{{notetag|1=35种语言分别为英语、瑞典语、挪威语、挪威语（尼诺斯克）、丹麦语、芬兰语、冰岛语、荷兰、德语、意大利语、西班牙语、葡萄牙语、葡萄牙语（巴西）、法语、波兰语、匈牙利语、希腊语、土耳其语、俄语、斯洛伐克语、加泰罗尼亚语、希伯来语、日本語、保加利亚语、爱沙尼亚、塞尔维亚语、阿拉伯语、﻿中文、捷克语、﻿斯洛文尼亚语、马来语、乌克兰语、孟加拉语、阿尔巴尼亚语和赫尔瓦语}}。

2009年4月，该网站的创始人（{{tsl|en|Peter Sunde||彼得·桑迪}}，{{tsl|sv|Fredrik Neij||弗雷德里克·内杰}}和{{tsl|en|Gottfrid Svartholm|哥特弗里德·斯瓦托姆|}}）在瑞典的{{tsl|en|The Pirate Bay trial||海盗湾审判}}中因[[盗版|涉嫌侵犯版权]]而被罚款并判处一年有期徒刑<ref name="appealdatepcw">{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/191304/article.html|title=Pirate Bay Appeals Looks Set to Start in September|author=Ricknäs|first=Mikael|date=2010-03-11|work={{tsl|sv|PC World||PC World}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160603074402/https://www.pcworld.com/article/191304/article.html|archivedate=2016-06-03|accessdate=}}</ref>。某些国家和地区的[[互联网服务供应商|互联网服务供应商]]已限制了对该网站的访问。随后，不断有提供访问服务的[[突破网络审查|代理网站]]出现<ref name="guardian_raid">{{Cite news|title=Swedish police raid sinks The Pirate Bay|author=Gibbs|first=Samuel|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2014-12-10|accessdate=2014-12-20|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/dec/10/swedish-police-raid-pirate-bay|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216140149/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/dec/10/swedish-police-raid-pirate-bay|archive-date=2014-12-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-18518777|title=The Pirate Bay 'breaches' BT's ban of the filesharing site|author=|first=|date=2012-06-22|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞|英國廣播公司新聞]]|accessdate=2015-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324162451/http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-18518777|archive-date=2015-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/aug/12/pirate-bay-piratebrowser-web-browser|title=Pirate Bay launches own PirateBrowser to evade ISP filesharing blocks|first=Stuart|author=Dredge|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2015-02-01|date=2013-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106232155/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/aug/12/pirate-bay-piratebrowser-web-browser|archive-date=2015-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。创始人在服刑期缩短后于2015年获释<ref name="theguardian June 2, 2015">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/jun/02/last-remaining-pirate-bay-founder-freed-from-jail-fredrik-neij|title=Last remaining Pirate Bay founder freed from jail|author=Gibbs|first=Samuel|date=2015-06-02|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|access-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206102327/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/jun/02/last-remaining-pirate-bay-founder-freed-from-jail-fredrik-neij|archive-date=2018-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

海盗湾引发了关于{{tsl|en|Legal aspects of file sharing||文件共享}}、[[著作權|版权]]和[[公民自由|公民自由]]等法律的争议和讨论，同时海盗湾逐渐成为了成为反对既定[[知识产权|知识产权]]法律和[[反著作權運動|反版权]]运动核心人物的政治举措的平台<ref name="Jessica L. Beyer.p.65">Jessica L. Beyer. ''Expect Us: Online Communities and Political Mobilization''. Page 65. [[牛津大學出版社|Oxford University Press]]. 3 July 2014. {{ISBN|9780199330751}}.</ref>。该网站面临多次关闭和域名缉获，转而使用一系列新网址继续运营<ref name="theguardian June 2, 20152">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/jun/02/last-remaining-pirate-bay-founder-freed-from-jail-fredrik-neij|title=Last remaining Pirate Bay founder freed from jail|author=Gibbs|first=Samuel|date=2015-06-02|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|access-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206102327/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/jun/02/last-remaining-pirate-bay-founder-freed-from-jail-fredrik-neij|archive-date=2018-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

海盗湾团队已经宣布需要进一步的权力下放，并将与 [https://github.com/globaldce/globaldce-gateway Globaldce]一起启动测试，以改善协作和审查抵抗力<ref>{{Cite web|title=https://twitter.com/torrentfreak/status/1523760420781563904|url=https://twitter.com/torrentfreak/status/1523760420781563904|access-date=2022-05-31|work=Twitter|language=zh}}</ref>。

== 运行历程 ==
海盜灣由[[瑞典|瑞典]]的民間[[反著作權|反版權]]組織{{tsl|en|Piratbyrån||海盜署}}於2003年成立，最初僅為[[瑞典語|瑞典語]]站點<ref>{{cite news |author = Ann Harrison |title = The Pirate Bay: Here to Stay? |date = 2006-03-13 |url = http://www.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2006/03/70358 |work = Wired News |accessdate = 2009-08-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131031053808/http://www.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2006/03/70358 |archive-date = 2013-10-31 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。後來發展成爲獨立的組織，2007年开始由{{tsl|en|Gottfrid Svartholm|哥特弗里德·斯瓦托姆}}、{{tsl|sv|Fredrik Neij||弗雷德里克·内杰}}與{{tsl|en|Peter Sunde|彼得·桑迪}}等人所營運<ref name="dashiji">{{cite web |language =  |publisher = [http://emulefans.com/ emulefans.com] |title = 海盗湾大事记 |url = http://emulefans.com/the-pirate-bay-events/ |author =  |date = 2010-05-20 |accessdate = 2010-10-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101122034819/http://emulefans.com/the-pirate-bay-events/ |archive-date = 2010-11-22 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

2008年1月，其同时在线人数突破1千万，网站上分享的种子数量超过100万，成为世界最大的BT网站<ref>{{cite news|author=Thomas Mennecke|title=The Pirate Bay Breaks 10 Million Users|date=2008-01-26|publisher=|url=http://www.slyck.com/story1643_The_Pirate_Bay_Breaks_10_Million_Users|work=Slyck News|pages=|accessdate=2008-01-28|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080128091037/http://www.slyck.com/story1643_The_Pirate_Bay_Breaks_10_Million_Users|archive-date=2008-01-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2009年4月17日，{{tsl|en|Peter Sunde||彼得·桑德}}，{{tsl|sv|Fredrik Neij||弗雷德里克·内杰}}，{{tsl|en|Gottfrid Svartholm|哥特弗里德·斯瓦托姆}}和{{tsl|en|Carl Lundström||卡尔·隆斯特罗姆}}因[[侵犯著作权|侵犯著作权]]被罚款3000万[[瑞典克朗|瑞典克朗]]（约4.2百万[[美元|美元]]），并被判一年有期徒刑<ref name="appealdatepcw" />。被告对判决提出上诉，并指控法官屈服于政治压力<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thelocal.se/20090417/18908|title=Pirate Bay guilty|author=|first=|date=2009-04-17|work={{tsl|en|The Local||The Local}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181230135909/https://www.thelocal.se/20090417/18908|archivedate=2018-12-30|accessdate=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年11月26日，瑞典上诉法院维持了判决，减少了原判，但罚款增加到4600万瑞典克朗<ref name="AppealVerdict">{{Cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20101126/tc_afp/swedeninternetpiracytrial|title=Prison terms of Pirate Bay executives' shortened|author=Devlin|first=Rita|date=2010-11-26|work=|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101128223235/http://news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20101126/tc_afp/swedeninternetpiracytrial|archivedate=2010-11-28|accessdate=2010-11-26|agency=[[法新社|法新社]]}}</ref>。2010年5月17日，由于法院对其[[带宽_(计算机)|带宽]]提供商的[[禁制令|禁令]]，网站开始无法访问<ref name="Injunction">{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/196501/Pirate_Bay.html|title=German Injunction Knocks The Pirate Bay Offline Temporarily|author=Essers|first=Loek|date=2010-05-17|work=[[PC_World|PC World]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120623160818/http://www.pcworld.com/article/196501/german_injunction_knocks_the_pirate_bay_offline_temporarily.html|archivedate=2012-06-23|accessdate=2010-05-18}}</ref>。

2011年5月起，{{tsl|en|Serious Tubes Networks||Serious Tubes Networks}}开始为海盗湾提供网络连接<ref name="torrentfreak-comcast">{{Cite news|date=2011-05-23|first=Ernesto|author=Van Der Sar|title=Comcast Offers Help to The Pirate Bay, Problems Fixed|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|url=https://torrentfreak.com/comcast-offers-help-to-the-pirate-bay-110512/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422025341/https://torrentfreak.com/comcast-offers-help-to-the-pirate-bay-110512/|archivedate=2014-04-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2012年2月29日起，海盗湾不再提供BT种子下载，全面转向[[磁力链接|磁力链接]]<ref name=":0" />。

2014年12月9日，海盗湾遭到{{tsl|en|Swedish Police Authority||瑞典警察}}的突袭，他们没收了服务器、计算机和其他设备<ref name="WRD-20141209">{{Cite web|author=Zetter|first=Kim|title=Pirate Bay Has Been Raided and Taken Down: Here's What We Know|url=https://www.wired.com/2014/12/pirate-bay-raided-taken-down/|date=2014-12-09|work=[[连线|连线]]|accessdate=2014-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210001152/http://www.wired.com/2014/12/pirate-bay-raided-taken-down/|archive-date=2014-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TF-20141209">{{Cite web|author=Username: Andy|title=Swedish Police Raid The Pirate Bay, Site Offline|url=https://torrentfreak.com/swedish-police-raid-the-pirate-bay-site-offline-141209/|date=2014-12-09|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|accessdate=2014-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209183613/https://torrentfreak.com/swedish-police-raid-the-pirate-bay-site-offline-141209/|archive-date=2014-12-09|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TV-20141210">{{Cite web|author=McCormick|first=Rich|title=The Pirate Bay goes offline after police raid server room – File-sharing site's homepage is mirrored at Costa Rica URL|url=https://www.theverge.com/2014/12/9/7364665/the-pirate-bay-goes-offline-after-police-raid-server-room|date=2014-12-10|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|accessdate=2014-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210102400/http://www.theverge.com/2014/12/9/7364665/the-pirate-bay-goes-offline-after-police-raid-server-room|archive-date=2014-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了海盗湾的论坛Suprbay.org之外，其他几个与种子有关的网站，包括{{tsl|en|EZTV||EZTV}}，{{tsl|en|Zoink||Zoink}}，[[Torrage|Torrage]]和Istole追踪器也被关闭<ref name="TF-20141209" />。在接下来的几天里，海盗湾的几个副本上线了，其中最著名的是由{{tsl|en|isoHunt||isoHunt}}创建的{{tsl|en|IsoHunt||oldpiratebay.org}}<ref name="BBC 2014-12-15">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-30477678|title=Pirate Bay 'copy' goes online after shutdown|publisher=[[英國廣播公司新聞|英國廣播公司新聞]]|date=2014-12-15|access-date=2019-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206120857/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-30477678|archive-date=2018-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Guard 2014-12-15">{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/dec/15/pirate-bay-revived-by-rival-piracy-site-torrent-isohunt|title=Pirate Bay revived by rival piracy site|work=[[衛報|衛報]]|date=2014-12-15|access-date=2019-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206102405/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/dec/15/pirate-bay-revived-by-rival-piracy-site-torrent-isohunt|archive-date=2018-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2015年5月19日，瑞典法院裁决扣押海盗湾的[[.se|.se]]域名<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.iis.se/english/news/se-acquitted-domain-names-not-to-be-forfeited-by-the-foundation/|title=SE acquitted – domain names not to be forfeited by the foundation | .SE|work=IIS.se|date=2015-05-19|accessdate=2015-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151029024732/https://www.iis.se/english/news/se-acquitted-domain-names-not-to-be-forfeited-by-the-foundation/|archive-date=2015-10-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/pirate-bay-down-key-domains-seized-but-site-likely-to-pop-back-up-again-elsewhere-10261815.html|title=Pirate Bay down: key domains seized, but site likely to pop back up again elsewhere|first=Andrew|author=Griffin|work=[[獨立報|獨立報]]|accessdate=2015-05-20|date=2015-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521105516/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/news/pirate-bay-down-key-domains-seized-but-site-likely-to-pop-back-up-again-elsewhere-10261815.html|archive-date=2015-05-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，海盗湾网站随后立刻新增了六个域名<ref>{{Cite web|date=2015-05-20|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/pirate-bay-seized-by-swedish-prosecutors-like-hydra-it-has-spawned-6-new-domains-1502150|title=Pirate Bay seized by Swedish prosecutors and like the hydra it has spawned 6 new domains|work=[[国际财经时报|国际财经时报]]|accessdate=2015-05-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150522221506/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/pirate-bay-seized-by-swedish-prosecutors-like-hydra-it-has-spawned-6-new-domains-1502150|archive-date=2015-05-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同时于2015年5月26日提出上诉<ref>{{Cite web|first=Linus|author=Larsson|url=http://www.dn.se/ekonomi/domen-om-piratebayse-overklagas/|title=Domen om piratebay.se överklagas|work={{tsl|en|Dagens Nyheter||Dagens Nyheter}}|publisher={{tsl|en|Bonnier AB||Bonnier AB}}s|date=2015-05-25|accessdate=2015-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150909170601/http://www.dn.se/ekonomi/domen-om-piratebayse-overklagas/|archive-date=2015-09-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年5月12日，上诉被驳回，法院裁定将这些域名移交给瑞典政府<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dn.se/ekonomi/hovratten-piratebayse-ska-agas-av-staten/|title=Hovrätten: Piratebay.se ska ägas av staten – DN.SE|author=|first=|date=2016-05-12|work=|language=sv|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206145533/https://www.dn.se/ekonomi/hovratten-piratebayse-ska-agas-av-staten/|archivedate=2018-12-06|accessdate=|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://torrentfreak.com/court-orders-pirate-bay-domains-forfeited-state-160512/|title=Court Orders Pirate Bay Domains to be Forfeited to the State|author=|first=|date=2016-05-12|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181206102623/https://torrentfreak.com/court-orders-pirate-bay-domains-forfeited-state-160512/|archivedate=2018-12-06|accessdate=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该网站于2016年5月恢复使用其原始的[[.org|.org]]域名<ref name="ibtimes2016-05-23">{{Cite web|url=https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/pirate-bay-loses-hydra-domains-returning-original-org-address-following-legal-challenges-1561515|title=Pirate Bay loses hydra and .se domains, returning to original .org address following legal challenges|author=Russon|first=Mary-Ann|date=2016-05-23|work=International Business Times UK|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160524120012/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/pirate-bay-loses-hydra-domains-returning-original-org-address-following-legal-challenges-1561515|archivedate=2016-05-24|accessdate=2016-05-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年8月，美国政府关闭了[[KickassTorrents|KickassTorrents]]，使得海盗湾再次成为访问量最大的BitTorrent网站<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://torrentfreak.com/pirate-bay-king-torrents-160814/|title=Pirate Bay is The King of Torrents Once Again|author=Van Der Sar|first=Ernesto|date=2016-08-14|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107040603/https://torrentfreak.com/pirate-bay-king-torrents-160814/|archivedate=2019-01-07|accessdate=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

