   | image2    = Thepiratebay.png
}}
海盗湾现今仅允许用户搜索[[磁力链接|磁力链接]]。这些链接可以通过[[對等網路|對等網路]]下载和共享资源<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2012/1/13/2703921/pirate-bay-torrent-file-magnet-links|title=The Pirate Bay set to kill torrent files, keep its service running with magnet links|author=Keene|first=Jamie|date=2012-01-13|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6BWzbw7JF?url=http://www.theverge.com/2012/1/13/2703921/pirate-bay-torrent-file-magnet-links|archivedate=2012-10-19|accessdate=2015-08-23}}</ref>。最初，海盗湾还允许用户下载[[种子文件|种子文件]]，这些小文件包含用户从其他用户下载数据文件所必需的[[元数据|元数据]]。[[种子文件|种子文件]]被分为几类：音频、视频、应用程序、游戏、色情和其他<ref name="browse">{{Cite web|url=https://thepiratebay.se/browse|title=Browse torrents|publisher=ThePirateBay.org|accessdate=2009-02-01|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140510112425/http://thepiratebay.se/browse|archivedate=2014-05-10}}</ref>。可以免费注册账户，注册时需要电子邮件地-{}-址，注册用户可以上传他们自己的种子和并对他人上传的种子评论。{{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}于2013年对海盗湾新上传的文件进行的一项研究显示，其中电视剧和电影占44％，色情片排在第二位，占35％，音频占上传量的9％<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://torrentfreak.com/35-of-all-pirate-bay-uploads-are-porn-140124/|title=35% of all Pirate Bay uploads are porn|first=Ernesto|author=Van Der Sar|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|date=2014-01-24|accessdate=2014-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330174031/http://torrentfreak.com/35-of-all-pirate-bay-uploads-are-porn-140124/|archivedate=2014-03-30}}</ref>。

在该网站上，用户能够轻松搜索音频、视频和游戏等类别，以及音频书籍、高分辨率电影和漫画等子类别的资源。自2012年1月起，它还为[[3D打印|3D打印]]对象提供了“Physibles”类别<ref>{{Cite web|author=Ludwig|first=Sean|title=The Pirate Bay launches crazy Physibles category for printing 3D objects|url=https://venturebeat.com/2012/01/24/pirate-bay-physibles-category-3d-printers/|accessdate=2015-06-04|date=2012-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150610022335/http://venturebeat.com/2012/01/24/pirate-bay-physibles-category-3d-printers/|archive-date=2015-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|author=Scott|first=Katie|title=The Pirate Bay adds 'physibles' 3D-printing category|url=https://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2012-01/24/pirate-bay-introduces-physibles|accessdate=2015-06-04|date=2012-01-24|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150605040650/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2012-01/24/pirate-bay-introduces-physibles|archivedate=2015-06-05}}</ref>。这些类别的内容可以按文件名、做种人数、下载人数或发布日期等进行排序。

=== 技术细节 ===
最初，海盗湾运行在四台[[Linux|Linux]][[服务器|服务器]]的Hypercube[[开源软件|开源]][[網頁伺服器|Web服务器]]上<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/3903397/hypercube_tracker_by_anakata|title=hypercube tracker by anakata|author=Username: JooiZe|date=2007-11-21|publisher=ThePirateBay.org|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422024214/https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/3903397/hypercube_tracker_by_anakata|archivedate=2014-04-22|accessdate=2015-08-23}}</ref>。2005年6月1日，海盗湾更新了其网站，以减少带宽使用量（据连线网报道，海盗湾的四个[[網頁伺服器|网络服务器]]中，每一个每一毫秒都会收到2个以上的[[超文本传输协议|HTTP]]请求<ref name="stay">{{Cite news|url=https://www.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2006/03/70358|title=The Pirate Bay: Here to Stay?|date=2006-03-13|first=Ann|author=Harrison|work=[[连线|连线]]|accessdate=2008-06-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031053808/http://www.wired.com/science/discoveries/news/2006/03/70358|archivedate=2013-10-31|deadurl=yes}}</ref>）；同时优化网站[[输入法|前端]]，创建更加用户友好的用户界面。该网站现在前端运行于[[Lighttpd|Lighttpd]]和[[PHP|PHP]]上，数据库后端采用[[MySQL|MySQL]]，两个站内搜索使用{{tsl|en|Sphinx (search engine)||Sphinx}}，使用[[Memcached|Memcached]]缓存SQL查询和PHP会话，在Lighttpd运行[[Varnish_cache|Varnish cache]]以缓存静态内容。截至2008年9月，Pirate Bay已拥有31个专用服务器，包括9个动态Web前端，一个数据库，两个搜索引擎和八个[[BitTorrent_tracker|Tracker服务器]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://static.thepiratebay.org/|title=Technical specifications|work=The Pirate Bay|accessdate=2008-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081108001121/http://static.thepiratebay.org/|archivedate=2008-11-08}}</ref>。

2007年12月7日，海盗湾完成了BitTorrent的[[tracker|tracker]]从Hypercube到[[Opentracker|Opentracker]]的迁移，也支持了之前无法在Hypercube中使用的基于[[用户数据报协议|UDP]]的Tracker协议<ref>{{Cite web|accessdate=2008-11-29|url=https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bay-switches-to-opentracker-071208/|title=The Pirate Bay Now Running on Opentracker|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|date=2007-12-08|first=Ernesto|author=Van Der Sar|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422025910/https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bay-switches-to-opentracker-071208/|archivedate=2014-04-22}}</ref>。

2008年6月，海盗湾宣布他们的服务器将支持[[傳輸層安全性協定|SSL]]加密，以回应瑞典新的窃听法<ref name="SlyckSSL">{{Cite web|url=http://www.slyck.com/story1691_SSL_Encrpytion_Coming_to_The_Pirate_Bay|title=SSL Encryption Coming to The Pirate Bay|author=Mennecke|first=Thomas|date=2008-06-22|publisher={{tsl|en|Slyck.com||Slyck.com}}|accessdate=2008-08-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422024604/http://www.slyck.com/story1691_SSL_Encrpytion_Coming_to_The_Pirate_Bay|archivedate=2014-04-22}}</ref><ref name="GuarSSL">{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/blog/2008/jun/23/thepiratebaywillusesslto|title=The Pirate Bay will use SSL to fight the law|author=Schofield|first=Jack|date=2008-06-23|work=[[衛報|衛報]] Blogs|accessdate=2010-06-13|location=London|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120411063930/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/blog/2008/jun/23/thepiratebaywillusesslto|archivedate=2012-04-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2009年1月19日，海盗湾使用仅支持IPv6的[[Opentracker|Opentracker]]版本为其tracker启用了[[IPv6|IPv6]]支持<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thepiratebay.se/blog/146|title=IPv6 support|author=Username: bkp|work=The Pirate Bay|date=2009-01-19|accessdate=2010-07-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422024324/https://thepiratebay.se/blog/146|archivedate=2014-04-22}}</ref>。2009年11月17日，海盗湾永久关闭其[[BitTorrent_tracker|Tracker服务器]]，声明不再需要中心化的Tracker，因为可以通过[[分散式雜湊表|分散式雜湊表]]（DHT）、[[节点交换|对等交换]]（PeX）和[[磁力链接|磁力链接]]等分散的方式找到并建立[[對等網路|P2P连接]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.slyck.com/story1880_The_Pirate_Bay_Trackers_Go_Offline_Forever|title=The Pirate Bay Trackers Go Offline Forever|date=2009-11-17|author=Mennecke|first=Thomas|publisher={{tsl|en|Slyck.com||Slyck.com}}|accessdate=2010-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140505015058/http://www.slyck.com/story1880_The_Pirate_Bay_Trackers_Go_Offline_Forever|archivedate=2014-05-05}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thelocal.se/23310/20091117/|title=Scrapping tracker may negate Pirate Bay fines|author=Landes|first=David|work={{tsl|en|The Local||The Local}}|date=2009-11-17|accessdate=2010-07-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123071147/http://www.thelocal.se/23310/20091117|archivedate=2013-01-23}}</ref>。

2012年2月29日起，海盗湾不再提供[[种子文件|种子文件]]下载，而只提供[[磁力链接|磁力链接]]。不到10人共享的Torrent文件将会被保留，以确保与可能不支持磁力链接的旧软件兼容<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bay-dumps-torrents-120228/|title=The Pirate Bay, Now Without Torrents|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|date=2012-02-28|accessdate=2012-03-02|first=Ernesto|author=Van Der Sar|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422025352/https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bay-dumps-torrents-120228/|archivedate=2014-04-22}}</ref>。网站上的公告补充说：“不再使用种子可以降低我们的成本，也会让我们的共同敌人更难阻止我们。”

=== 广告 ===
自2006年以来，海盗湾就开始通过站内搜索结果页面上展示的广告获得资金。根据{{tsl|sv|Svenska Dagbladet||Svenska Dagbladet}}的估计，这些广告每月能产生约600,000[[瑞典克朗|瑞典克朗]]（84,000美元）的收入<ref>{{Cite web|date=2006-07-08|url=http://www.svd.se/nyheter/inrikes/pirate-bay-drar-in-miljonbelopp_334410.svd|title=Pirate Bay drar in miljonbelopp|first=Staffan|author=Olsson|language=sv|work={{tsl|en|Svenska Dagbladet||Svenska Dagbladet}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101002110851/http://www.svd.se/nyheter/inrikes/pirate-bay-drar-in-miljonbelopp_334410.svd|archivedate=2010-10-02|accessdate=2010-10-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2006-07-08|url=http://rixstep.com/1/20060708,00.shtml|title=TPB Raking in Millions|work=Rixstep|accessdate=2009-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080721083213/http://rixstep.com/1/20060708,00.shtml|archive-date=2008-07-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2006年的一项调查中，警方得出结论，海盗湾每年能从广告中获得1.2百万瑞典克朗（169,000美元）的收入<ref>{{Cite news|first=Ivar|author=Andersen|title=Rättegången mot The pirate bay: Åklagaren yrkar på fängelse|work=Fria Tidningen|language=sv|date=2009-03-02|url=http://www.fria.nu/artikel/78204|access-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180827080849/http://www.fria.nu/artikel/78204|archive-date=2018-08-27|dead-url=no}}([https://translate.google.com/translate?u=http%3A//www.fria.nu/artikel/78204&hl=en&langpair=auto%7Cen&tbb=1&ie=UTF-8 English tr.] {{Wayback|url=https://translate.google.com/translate?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fria.nu%2Fartikel%2F78204&hl=en&langpair=auto%7Cen&tbb=1&ie=UTF-8 |date=20200717001023 }})</ref>。检方在2009年的审判中通过电子邮件和截图估计，海盗湾每年的广告收入超过1000万瑞典克朗（140万美元）<ref>{{Cite web|date=2009-03-02|first=Sam|author=Sundberg|title=TPB har tjänat tio miljoner om året|url=http://blog.svd.se/thepiratebay/2009/03/02/tpb-har-tjanat-tio-miljoner-om-aret/|work={{tsl|en|Svenska Dagbladet||Svenska Dagbladet}} Blogs|language=sv|accessdate=2012-12-22|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6D8mmNnUX?url=http://blog.svd.se/thepiratebay/2009/03/02/tpb-har-tjanat-tio-miljoner-om-aret/|archivedate=2012-12-24}}</ref>，但起诉书使用了先前警方调查的估计数<ref>{{Cite web|first=Oscar|author=Swartz|date=2009-03-02|title=Var är mina tio miljoner?|url=http://nyheter24.se/nyheter/blogg/oscar-swartz/146685-swartz-var-ar-mina-tio-miljoner|work=Nyheter24|language=sv|accessdate=2009-04-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090306121207/http://nyheter24.se/nyheter/blogg/oscar-swartz/146685-swartz-var-ar-mina-tio-miljoner|archivedate=2009-03-06}}</ref>。

2008年，[[國際唱片業協會|IFPI]]声称海盗湾更多地是在赚取利润而不是支-{}-持人们的权利<ref name="arsfabricated">{{Cite news|date=2008-02-01|first=Ryan|author=Paul|accessdate=2008-09-29|url=https://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/news/2008/02/pirate-bay-big-revenue-claims-fabricated-by-prosecutors.ars|title=Pirate Bay: big revenue claims fabricated by prosecutors|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112114058/http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/news/2008/02/pirate-bay-big-revenue-claims-fabricated-by-prosecutors.ars|archivedate=2012-01-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>。海盗湾声称这些指控并不属实，该网站的发言人{{tsl|en|Peter Sunde|彼得·桑迪}}声称，海盗湾网站的高带宽、电力和硬件成本减少了其盈利的潜力，甚至可能会亏本运营<ref name="arsfabricated" />。在2009年的审判中，辩方估计该网站的年度支出为800,000瑞典克朗（110,000美元）<ref name="kuprijanko">{{Cite news|first=Alexander|author=Kuprijanko|title=Försvaret: verksamheten är laglig|work=[[南瑞典日報|南瑞典日報]]|language=sv|date=2009-03-03|url=http://sydsvenskan.se/sverige/article417153/Forsvaret-verksamheten-ar-laglig.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318044057/http://sydsvenskan.se/sverige/article417153/Forsvaret-verksamheten-ar-laglig.html|archivedate=2009-03-18}} ([https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=auto&tl=en&u=http%3A%2F%2Fsydsvenskan.se%2Fsverige%2Farticle417153%2FForsvaret-verksamheten-ar-laglig.html English tr.] {{Wayback|url=https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=auto&tl=en&u=http%3A%2F%2Fsydsvenskan.se%2Fsverige%2Farticle417153%2FForsvaret-verksamheten-ar-laglig.html |date=20200506070312 }})</ref>。

== 资金 ==
=== 早期融资 ===
2007年4月，瑞典脱口秀Bert证实了海盗湾获得了右翼企业家{{tsl|en|Carl Lundström|Carl Lundström}}的资金支-{}-持。海盗湾的发言人Tobias Andersson承认，“如果没有Lundström的支-{}-持，海盗湾将无法运作”，并表示大部分资金都用于购买服务器和带宽<ref name="Regrightwing">{{Cite web|accessdate=2008-09-28|url=https://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/05/07/pirate_bay_accepted_right_wing_money/|title=The Pirate Bay admits links with right-wing benefactor|work=[[The_Register|The Register]]|date=2007-05-07|author=Jibbenga|first=Jan|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220113743/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2007/05/07/pirate_bay_accepted_right_wing_money/|archivedate=2013-12-20}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|first=Konrad|author=Lischka|date=2007-05-04|url=http://www.spiegel.de/netzwelt/web/0,1518,480972,00.html|title=Piratenseite im Zwielicht: Rechtspopulist finanziert Internet-Tauschbörse|work=[[明镜|明镜]]|language=de|accessdate=2008-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080915081006/http://www.spiegel.de/netzwelt/web/0,1518,480972,00.html|archive-date=2008-09-15|dead-url=no}} ([https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=auto&tl=en&u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Fnetzwelt%2Fweb%2F0%2C1518%2C480972%2C00.html English tr.] {{Wayback|url=https://translate.google.com/translate?hl=en&sl=auto&tl=en&u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spiegel.de%2Fnetzwelt%2Fweb%2F0%2C1518%2C480972%2C00.html |date=20200506070326 }})</ref>。

=== 捐赠 ===
从2004年到2006年，海盗湾开放捐赠页面以接受捐赠，其中列出了多种付款方式，并为捐赠者提供一定时间的福利，例如没有广告和Tracker会员<ref>{{Cite web|title=Donations|work=The Pirate Bay|url=https://thepiratebay.se/donate.php|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041009174905/http://thepiratebay.org/donate.php|archivedate=2004-10-09|accessdate=2012-10-17}}{{Cite web|title=Donations|work=The Pirate Bay|url=https://thepiratebay.se/donate.php|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060702224038/http://thepiratebay.org/donate.php|archivedate=2006-07-02|accessdate=2012-10-17}}</ref>。之后，捐赠页面被改为“您可捐赠给您当地的专业盗版组织”<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thepiratebay.se/donate.php|title=Donations|work=The Pirate Bay|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060806112626/http://thepiratebay.org/donate.php|archivedate=2006-08-06|accessdate=2012-10-17}}</ref>，后来被改为重定向到网站的主页面<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://thepiratebay.org/|title=The Pirate Bay (main page)|work=The Pirate Bay|accessdate=2017-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171110063318/https://thepiratebay.org/|archive-date=2017-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年，瑞典政治真人秀节目顶级候选人（Toppkandidaterna）的候选人{{tsl|sv|Petter Nilsson||Petter Nilsson}}向海盗湾捐赠了35,000瑞典克朗（4,925.83美元），用于购买新服务器<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thepiratebay.se/blog/25|title=The First State Financed Tracker|author=Username: tbz|work=TPB Blog|publisher=The Pirate Bay|date=2006-05-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100123051531/http://thepiratebay.org/blog/25|archivedate=2010-01-23|accessdate=2012-10-17}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Petter vann 'Toppkandidaterna' |language=sv|date=2006-03-13|work={{tsl|en|Dagens Nyheter||Dagens Nyheter}}|publisher={{tsl|en|Bonnier AB||Bonnier AB}}s|url=http://www.dn.se/kultur-noje/film-tv/petter-vann-toppkandidaterna|accessdate=2012-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150605232526/http://www.dn.se/kultur-noje/film-tv/petter-vann-toppkandidaterna/|archive-date=2015-06-05|dead-url=no}}{{Cite web|title=Reality-stjerne giver præmie til fildelere|language=da|work={{tsl|sv|PC World||PC World}}|publisher=[[国际数据集团|国际数据集团]]|date=2006-03-14|url=http://www.pcworld.dk/art/7189/reality-stjerne-giver-praemie-til-fildelere|accessdate=2017-11-10|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717001128/https://www.dn.se/kultur-noje/film-tv/petter-vann-toppkandidaterna/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007年，海盗湾设立了一个旨在购买[[西兰公国|西兰公国]]的基金（这是一个未被国际承认的[[私人国家|私人国家]]），并声称未来这个国家可以接入高速互联网而且没有版权法<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bay-to-buy-sealand/|accessdate=2017-11-10|title=The Pirate Bay Wants to Buy Sealand|work={{tsl|en|TorrentFreak||TorrentFreak}}|date=2007-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422025109/https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bay-to-buy-sealand/|archive-date=2014-04-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2009年，当时被法院定罪的海盗湾创始人要求用户停止为其罚款捐款，因为他们拒绝支付法院的罚金<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tomshardware.com/news/pirate-bay-torrent-download,7582.html|title=Pirate Bay: No Donations! We're Not Paying|author=McEntegart|first=Jane|date=2009-04-21|work=[[Tom's_硬體指南|Tom's 硬體指南]]|archiveurl=|archivedate=|accessdate=2017-11-10}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2009-04-19|title=TPB FTW|work=TPB Blog|publisher=The Pirate Bay|url=https://thepiratebay.se/blog/151|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090429213041/http://thepiratebay.org/blog/151|archivedate=2009-04-29|accessdate=2012-10-19}}</ref>。2013年，海盗湾在网站首页上发布了[[比特币|比特币]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://medium.com/@theinfovalley097/what-is-rarbg-622d14f1ec47/|first=Philippa|author=Warr|title=The Pirate Bay now accepting Bitcoin donations|work=[[连线|连线]]|date=2013-04-23|accessdate=2013-04-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422031450/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2013-04/23/bitcoin-pirate-bay|archivedate=2014-04-22}}</ref>以及[[莱特币|莱特币]]地址<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thepiratebay.se|title=The Pirate Bay|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6DBfvO5v5?url=http://thepiratebay.se/|archivedate=2012-12-26}} homepage.</ref>来接受捐款。

== 事件 ==
=== 遭受黑客攻击 ===
2007年5月，海盗湾遭到了[[黑客_(计算机安全)|黑客]]的攻击<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://thepiratebay.se/blog/68|title=User data stolen but not unsecured|author=Username: bkp|work=TPB Blog|publisher=The Pirate Bay|date=2007-05-11|accessdate=2008-09-28|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/652XjtLuu?url=https://thepiratebay.org/blog|archivedate=2012-01-28}}</ref>。他们复制了包括约一百五十万用户信息的数据库。海盗湾向其用户声称这些数据没有任何价值，因为其中的密码和电子邮件都经过[[加密|加密]]和[[散列函數|散列]]。一些博客表示，一个名为AUH（{{lang|sv|Arga Unga Hackare}}，意为“愤怒的年轻黑客”）的团体可能是这次攻击的发起人，但AUH在瑞典报纸《{{le|计算机世界 (瑞典)|Computerworld|计算机世界}}》上表示他们并没有参与其中，不对这次攻击负责<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://computersweden.idg.se/2.2683/1.107659/|title="AUH inte bakom hacket" – Computer Sweden|work=ComputerSweden.IDG.se|publisher=[[国际数据集团|国际数据集团]]|date=2007-05-11|accessdate=2010-12-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213234329/http://computersweden.idg.se/2.2683/1.107659/|archivedate=2013-12-13}}</ref>。

2009年4月27日，海盗湾网站[[IPv4|IPv4]]的访问开始出现异常。人们普遍猜测这是瑞典[[盗版|反盗版]]组织实行的强制停运。当时仍可通过IPv6访问网站及论坛<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://suprbay.org/showthread.php?t=32588&page=46|title=The Pirate Bay - fiber cut|publisher=Suprbay.org|accessdate=2009-04-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090601224043/http://suprbay.org/showthread.php?t=32588&page=46|archivedate=2009-06-01}}</ref>。

=== 网站更名 ===

2008年，[[国际奥林匹克委员会|国际奥委会]]向瑞典司法部长写信要求瑞典政府提供帮助，阻止海盗湾分发[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会|北京奥运会]]视频片段。瑞典政府回应其已对海盗湾提起了侵权诉讼，但开庭时间未定。然而，海盗湾除了暂时将网站重命名为北京湾外，并没有采取任何措施<ref>{{Cite news|accessdate=2008-09-29|url=https://www.wired.com/threatlevel/2008/08/irate-bay-renam|title=Pirate Bay Renamed Beijing Bay After Olympics Tracking|work=[[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]]|date=2008-08-18|author=Kravets|first=David|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107202638/http://www.wired.com/threatlevel/2008/08/irate-bay-renam|archivedate=2012-11-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2009年伊朗推特革命（也称[[伊朗绿色革命|伊朗绿色革命]]）时，海盗湾将其主页改名为“波斯湾”，海盗船变为[[绿色|绿色]]，以此声援伊朗民众<ref name="Mottahedeh 2009">{{cite web|last=Mottahedeh|first=Negar|title=Hashtag Solidarity in Iran|website=Stanford University Press Blog|date=2009-06-12|url=https://stanfordpress.typepad.com/blog/2015/06/hashtag-solidarity-in-iran.html|access-date=2019-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706160547/http://stanfordpress.typepad.com/blog/2015/06/hashtag-solidarity-in-iran.html|archive-date=2018-07-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此外，海盗湾还曾改名为九头蛇湾、海盗船湾、自由湾、凤凰湾、磁铁湾、侠盗猎车湾等名称，并在其站内的涂鸦板块上发布了对应的一系列Logo<ref>{{cite web|title=The Pirate Bay's Rebellious History|website=TorrentFreak|date=2018-04-29|url=https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bays-rebellious-history-in-doodles-180429/|access-date=2019-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190202154043/https://torrentfreak.com/the-pirate-bays-rebellious-history-in-doodles-180429/|archive-date=2019-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The Pirate Bay 2015">{{cite web | title=The galaxy's most resilient bittorrent site | website=The Pirate Bay | date=2015-05-28 | url=https://thepiratebay.org/doodles | access-date=2019-02-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181231163838/https://thepiratebay.org/doodles | archive-date=2018-12-31 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。
<gallery mode="packed" heights="175px">
